"title": "8348: spiritual growth, nature of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8348",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Having given spiritual life to his people, God expects them to grow to maturity.</p>\n<h2>God desires the spiritual growth of his people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:48\">MAT 5:48</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:1\">HEB 6:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:9-2Cor13:11\">2CO 13:9–13:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:4\">EPH 1:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:10\">EPH 2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:17-Eph3:19\">EPH 3:17–3:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:12\">PHP 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:1\">1TH 4:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:7\">1TH 4:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:9\">2TI 1:9</a></p>\n<h2>Christlikeness is the goal of spiritual growth</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:29\">ROM 8:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:13-Eph4:15\">EPH 4:13–4:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:5\">PHP 2:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:2-1John3:3\">1JN 3:2–3:3</a></p>\n<h2>Aspects of spiritual growth</h2>\n<h3>Growth in grace</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:18\">2PE 3:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov4:18\">PRO 4:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:1-1Pet2:3\">1PE 2:1–2:3</a></p>\n<h3>Growth in faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:3\">2TH 1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor10:15\">2CO 10:15</a></p>\n<h3>Growth in love</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:12\">1TH 3:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:5\">ROM 5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:1\">1CO 14:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:9\">PHP 1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:9-1Thess4:10\">1TH 4:9–4:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:24\">HEB 10:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:7-1John4:21\">1JN 4:7–4:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:1-1John5:3\">1JN 5:1–5:3</a></p>\n<h3>Growth in understanding</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:27\">PSA 119:27</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:20\">1CO 14:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:97-Ps119:99\">PSA 119:97–119:99</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:2\">ROM 12:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:19\">ROM 16:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:11\">1CO 13:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:17-Eph1:19\">EPH 1:17–1:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:9-Phil1:10\">PHP 1:9–1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:9\">COL 1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:14\">HEB 5:14</a></p>\n<h3>Growth in holiness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:1\">2CO 7:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:25-Eph5:26\">EPH 5:25–5:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:11\">HEB 2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:10-Heb10:14\">HEB 10:10–10:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:14\">HEB 12:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:12\">HEB 13:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:15-1Pet1:16\">1PE 1:15–1:16</a></p>\n<h3>Growth in fruitfulness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:16\">JHN 15:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:23\">MAT 13:23</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:20\">MRK 4:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:15\">LUK 8:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:2\">JHN 15:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:8\">JHN 15:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:11\">PHP 1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:10\">COL 1:10</a></p>\n<h3>Growth in contentment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:11-Phil4:12\">PHP 4:11–4:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:6\">1TI 6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:5\">HEB 13:5</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of spiritual growth</h2>\n<h3>In individuals</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:26\">1SA 2:26</a> <em>Samuel</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:80\">LUK 1:80</a> <em>John the Baptist</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:40\">LUK 2:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:52\">LUK 2:52</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:22\">ACT 9:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:26-1Cor9:27\">1CO 9:26–9:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:12-Phil3:14\">PHP 3:12–3:14</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:26\">ACT 18:26</a> <em>Apollos</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:11\">PHM 1:11</a> <em>Onesimus</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:2-3John1:3\">3JN 1:2–1:3</a> <em>Gaius</em></p>\n<h3>In the church</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:31\">ACT 9:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:26\">ACT 11:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:5\">ACT 16:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor10:15\">2CO 10:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:6\">COL 1:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:13\">1TH 2:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:3\">2TH 1:3</a></p>",
